3206467537011", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/468752496_523206470870344_633342755118363834_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i5XvThash2sQ7kNvgEZXV7L&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAGHcuP_He7oOHb-SjkWZh3L83FbZE4_zBxQUOXwMWSVQ&oe=677CFA63"}, "display_name": "Attack on Titan VR: Unbreakable - Part.1", "keywords": ["AttackonTitan", "AoT", "Shingeki", "Action", "Hunting"], "long_description": "---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n{1742353936601045}\n{2026049414581724}\n# Complete Edition (Part.1 + 2) Available Now!\n\nPrepare for combat with Omni-Directional Mobility Gear and fly head-first into battle! Defy all odds and eliminate the Titans!\n\nAttack on Titan VR: Unbreakable, the first-person action-adventure VR platformer based on the highly acclaimed manga \u201cAttack on Titan\u201d and the latest installment of the VR series. \n\n{1280368342833344}\n\n\nJoin the Scout Regiment as an aspiring recruit and help defend mankind from the Titan invasion.\n\n\n# Omni-Directional Mobility Gear\nUtilize the Omni-Directional Mobility Gear to maneuver through the air and combat the onslaught of Titans! \n{1195760871453526}\n\n\n# The Titan Threat\nTitans rely on their instincts to hunt humans and satisfy their insatiable appetites.\nOvercome the fear of death and lay waste to the Titan army!\n{1042373100565202}\n\n\n# Distinct Weapons\nEach weapon offers unique characteristics that can alter the course of battle and how it is approached!\n{469443659357575}\n\n\n\n**Additionally, the Thunder Spear Unlock Event is on the horizon. Join forces with Scouts from around the world and prepare to take on this global challenge.**\n\n\n\u00a9 Hajime Isayama / Kodansha Ltd. \u00a9 UNIVRS, Inc.\n", "short_description": "Complete Edition (Part.1 + 2) Available 